1. General

What is this service?
This is a sample AI-powered voice assistant. It can answer questions, look up account information, and help with common tasks.

How do I get started?
Simply call the number and speak naturally. The assistant understands conversational language and will guide you.

What can the assistant help me with?
The assistant can answer product questions, check account status, and connect you with a human agent if needed.

Is my information secure?
Yes. All calls are handled over encrypted connections and your data is never stored beyond the session.

2. Account Services

How do I check my account balance?
Just ask "What's my balance?" and the assistant will look it up for you.

How do I update my contact information?
The assistant can help you update your phone number or email. You may need to verify your identity first.

What happens if I forget my PIN?
The assistant can guide you through the account recovery process or connect you with a human agent.

3. Support

How do I speak to a human?
Say "I'd like to speak to a human" or "transfer me to an agent" at any time.

What are your support hours?
Our AI assistant is available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. Human agents are available Monday through Friday, 9 AM to 6 PM.

How do I report a problem?
Tell the assistant about the issue and it will either resolve it directly or escalate to the appropriate team.
